<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_eeb40fa1-7f31-40f8-a13d-485f95145e7c" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/></meta><sptc>H3V2</sptc><title id="_05b3b670-4f61-4a79-8f19-88f01b4d68c6">Avoidance of spread of fire from allotment boundary</title><archive-num>2019: V2.3.1.2</archive-num><subclause id="_2f57c21e-a7a7-4aad-928a-18f6d51ba7e8" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_945b50e9-7d6b-42d0-8c81-b9a2079641a8">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Compliance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1869_0.14.0.xml#_3357b0a1-56c1-4eb3-9d07-cd7e68edee1b" id="_3bf03241-0e2c-48a4-9271-0a9e674b6440" scope="local" type="subclause">H3P1(1)(b)</xref> to avoid the spread of fire from an allotment boundary is verified when—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_8a9d4ff9-4644-4fa4-bd91-2d302e1dc09a">the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1267_2.3.0.xml#_d87c7cc0-d0b0-40ab-9a5b-d070ed6e115e" id="_c559649f-f1cf-4d0a-8b43-9c2c5b7c1ce9" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">external walls</xref> and any openings in the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1267_2.3.0.xml#_d87c7cc0-d0b0-40ab-9a5b-d070ed6e115e" id="_c9387477-2556-41de-b822-e9e354991e47" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">external walls</xref> of a building, less than 0.9 m from an allotment boundary, are capable of withstanding 92.6 kW/m<sup id="_20c8a3db-cdec-4778-aa0d-c8d061d7547c">2</sup> of heat flux for 60 minutes; and</li><li id="_b1e61896-2177-4ee7-86f5-abfd63555720">the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1267_2.3.0.xml#_d87c7cc0-d0b0-40ab-9a5b-d070ed6e115e" id="_1766e994-c754-4c83-b83e-b961f424def1" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">external walls</xref> extend to the underside of a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1377_5.9.0.xml#_be8a1d10-4119-4eb0-a014-07a806b104ff" id="_8a09befa-bf1e-46af-b533-526501e6f16f" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-combustible</xref> roof covering or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1377_5.9.0.xml#_be8a1d10-4119-4eb0-a014-07a806b104ff" id="_092d1a86-5a65-4571-8c69-a47db6dfa314" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">non-combustible</xref> eaves lining in accordance with clause <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/1848#_263a5890-898c-4938-a6e8-4bd931480b0f" id="_f2f62d44-7822-478a-b866-27100d416b19" publishing-id="housing" scope="external" type="clause">9.2.3</xref> of the ABCB Housing Provisions.</li></ol></subclause></clause>